your statement in the morning

34:27.232 --> 34:29.733
and checked your ID.
Just formalities.

34:31.837 --> 34:36.373
Well, I feel really reassured
that you're gonna be here,

34:36.375 --> 34:37.774
Officer...

34:37.776 --> 34:41.411
- Uh, Dean.
- Dean.

34:44.349 --> 34:46.583
After all I've been through.

34:54.660 --> 34:57.527
Well, I've, um--

34:57.529 --> 35:01.698
I've gone and got myself
an errant nine on the top line.

35:01.700 --> 35:03.767
Are you any good
at "Suduku"?

35:07.372 --> 35:09.172
( Japanese accent )
Sudoku.

35:09.174 --> 35:10.607
( chuckles )

35:15.714 --> 35:17.714
Do you know,
I'll have a go at this
for you, officer,

35:17.716 --> 35:23.386
if you could get me
a little chocolate biscuit
or something?

35:23.388 --> 35:26.556
Hot drink? Anything?

35:26.558 --> 35:30.460
Call me Luke, now that
we're sharing a "Sudoku."

35:33.265 --> 35:35.465
- ( muttering )
- Yeah, a crisp.

35:47.479 --> 35:49.579
