but I have things I need
to get back for.

35:49.581 --> 35:51.281
Oh, really? Do you, Statton?

35:51.283 --> 35:52.816
You sleep on
your wife's sofa bed.

35:52.818 --> 35:54.584
What were your
big plans tonight,

35:54.586 --> 35:56.353
to go home
and jerk off and cry?

35:56.355 --> 35:59.589
- Jerk off and cry?
- Jerk off and cry.

35:59.591 --> 36:02.259
- Fuck off and die.
- Oh, come on!

36:02.261 --> 36:04.761
Isn't a part of you
enjoying that something's
happening to you?

36:04.763 --> 36:06.930
- No!
- Wouldn't you like
to have one story

36:06.932 --> 36:09.232
that didn't end with,
"And there was a cat

36:09.234 --> 36:10.734
trapped in my piano
all along?"

36:10.736 --> 36:12.936
You loved that story!
You laughed at that story--

36:12.938 --> 36:15.205
that story got you
into my bed!

36:15.207 --> 36:18.742
That story made me realize
that you needed to get laid.

36:20.312 --> 36:22.612
And you know what else?

36:22.614 --> 36:24.781
At the hotel,

36:24.783 --> 36:29.619
I left the door
unlocked deliberately

36:29.621 --> 36:33.623
because
it's more exciting that way.

36:33.625 --> 36:37.394
You fucked up nun!
You fucked up fucking nun!

36:40.299 --> 36:43.466
Mm-hmm.
Yup, yup, yup.

36:43.468 --> 36:44.734
Well, this seems
to be the room,

36:44.736 --> 36:47.337
that makes you
the clients.

36:47.339 --> 36:48.939
Are you our lawyer?

36:48.941 --> 36:51.808
- Yeah. Yup.
- Can I get some ice please?

36:51.810 --> 36:56.346
I doubt it. No.
The facilities here
are surprisingly two-star.

36:56.348 --> 36:58.481
- I'm really hurt.
- No shit.

36:58.483 --> 37:00.217
So, tell me
how innocent you are.

37:00.219 --> 37:02.385
How the cops
have got it all wrong.

37:02.387 --> 37:03.520
They have got it all wrong.

37:03.522 --> 37:05.655
Okay, Yvonne,
I'm listening.

37:05.657 --> 37:07.357
I prefer Carol.

37:07.359 --> 37:08.992
Or Mary or countless
other names.

37:08.994 --> 37:10.493
Always reassures the court
if you have a number

37:10.495 --> 37:11.628
of functional pseudonyms.

37:11.630 --> 37:13.263
Yvonne will do.

37:13.265 --> 37:15.665
Yeah. Yup, yup, yup.

37:15.667 --> 37:18.835
Well, I'm Rich.
Uh, name only.

37:18.837 --> 37:20.670
Obviously,
not literally rich

37:20.672 --> 37:22.539
or I'd be drunk
this time of night.

37:22.541 --> 37:25.375
Look, these guys,
they stole my watch,
they stole my identity.

37:25.377 --> 37:28.011
Yup, yup, yup.
Well, I think I have enough.

37:28.013 --> 37:29.813
- You don't have a enough.
- They held us and gunpoint.

37:29.815 --> 37:31.281
I have enough
to get you bail.

37:31.283 --> 37:32.916
But you don't need bail
in the UK.

37:32.918 --> 37:34.484
This is not the UK.

37:34.486 --> 37:36.686
It's an island
Crown dependency.

37:36.688 --> 37:38.788
You can get to
the mainland on a rowboat.

37:38.790 --> 37:42.759
You need bail.
So, who do I call?

37:42.761 --> 37:45.028
- I don't know.
- No one springs to mind.

37:45.030 --> 37:46.296
Me neither.

37:48.700 --> 37:49.899
Okay.

37:52.404 --> 37:55.905
Tell me a very,
very interesting story.

37:58.877 --> 38:01.544
Hello, Danno.
Look, I'm sorry it's so late.

38:01.546 --> 38:03.713
Uh, it's Statton.

38:03.715 --> 38:06.549
Yeah, right back to you.
Yeah, fine, fine.

38:06.551 --> 38:09.886
How are you?
Uh, look, sorry, mate,
I need to get to the point.

38:09.888 --> 38:13.056
Do you remember a guy
called Kipper from your party?

38:13.058 --> 38:15.725
Yeah, do you know
his surname?

38:15.727 --> 38:20.063
- Oh, no, he doesn't know.
- Give me that.

38:20.065 --> 38:23.733
Danno, are you Catholic?

38:23.735 --> 38:25.902
Well, I'm a virgin
motherfucking nun

38:25.904 --> 38:28.305
and I need you to
reach back down there

38:28.307 --> 38:31.574
into you subconscious
and figure the fuck out
what Kipper's last name is

38:31.576 --> 38:34.744
or I'll personally see to it
that you're stuck in Purgatory

38:34.746 --> 38:37.914
for the duration of your
natural born death!

38:37.916 --> 38:39.582
Whew! Oof.

38:39.584 --> 38:40.750
Yup.

38:43.522 --> 38:45.555
Motherfucker.

38:46.792 --> 38:49.926
( all inhale )

38:49.928 --> 38:52.462
Get the hospital
on the phone now.

38:52.464 --> 38:54.364
Right. What was
his sidekick's name?

38:54.366 --> 38:57.967
I don't remember.
I'm not very good
with names.

38:59.471 --> 39:01.838
They did say.
I did a mnemonic.

39:01.840 --> 39:03.073
You used my mnemonics?

39:03.075 --> 39:05.108
I pictured the Titanic.

39:05.110 --> 39:06.876
Rearranging deck chairs
on the Titanic.

39:06.878 --> 39:08.511
His name is Deck Chair!

39:08.513 --> 39:09.646
Dec. Short for Declan.

39:09.648 --> 39:10.647
Dec, Dec.
His name's Dec.

39:10.649 --> 39:11.915
Uh...

39:13.618 --> 39:16.519
Yeah, Kipper's gone.

39:16.521 --> 39:18.621
He walked out
of the hospital

39:18.623 --> 39:22.025
when Officer Dean
went to get him
a chocolate bickie.

39:23.962 --> 39:25.628
Go and make up
a better story

39:25.630 --> 39:27.797
of how this criminal
got away.

39:27.799 --> 39:30.133
