for me when I was born

45:54.519 --> 45:58.888
and I've never taken it off
since I've had it.

45:58.890 --> 46:01.357
- Not before tonight.
- Oh.

46:01.359 --> 46:03.359
And I know you think
it's just stupid

46:03.361 --> 46:05.027
