1:17:34.083 --> 1:17:35.416
I'll definitely keep
in touch, though, eh?

1:17:35.418 --> 1:17:37.151
Hmm.

1:17:41.791 --> 1:17:43.924
- Take this.
- Oh.

1:17:43.926 --> 1:17:46.661
